import React from 'react'; import { useHistory } from 'react-router-dom' import './navbuttons.css' import Champaigns from './campaignHolder/campaignHolder' import EmailLists from './emailListHolder/emailListHolder' import { useSpring, animated } from 'react-spring' import store from '../../store/store' const NavButtons = () => { const uname = store.getState().userData.username const { push } = useHistory(null) const [logoffButtonStyle, setLogOffButtonStyle] = useSpring(() => ({ flexBasis: "12%", backgroundColor: "#3a4782ff", text: uname, svgMargin: "4%", // pdis: "flex" })) return ( <>
setLogOffButtonStyle({ flexBasis: "12%", backgroundColor: "#606060ff", text: "Logoff", svgMargin: "4%", })} onMouseLeave={() => setLogOffButtonStyle({ flexBasis: "12%", backgroundColor: "#3a4782ff", text: uname, svgMargin: "4%", })} onClick={() => { push('/') localStorage.clear() }} > {uname}
Champaigns
Email Lists
{/*
push("/dashboard/newcamp")} > Create Champaign
Add Emaillist
*/}
); } export default NavButtons;
